;;; bcp-hymnal-1940-recordings.el --- Tune-keyed YouTube recordings  -*- lexical-binding: t; -*-

;;; Commentary:

;; Maps registered Hymnal 1940 tune-id symbols to YouTube video URLs
;; from the "Episcopal 1940 Hymnal" piano playlist
;; (https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZZAT1pP5dJrWsu25T4gVyIAC8nOI-lP8),
;; an instrumental playthrough of every tune in the Hymnal 1940.
;; Because the recordings are instrumental, we key by tune (not by
;; hymn slot): a single tune has a single recording regardless of
;; which text is set to it.
;;
;; URLs are pointers to the channel; we host nothing, fetch nothing
;; at runtime.  The renderer uses these to render each "Tune:" name
;; as a clickable link that invokes `browse-url'.
;;
;; Coverage: 586 of the 642 registered tunes.  Missing entries are
;; either tunes that lack a video on the channel, foreign-spelling
;; aliases the matcher couldn't resolve, or canticle-style entries
;; outside the hymn-tune corpus.

;;; Code:

